we area going to select "File"

00:02:49.189 --> 00:02:56.189
and create "new event"

00:02:59.279 --> 00:03:01.809
we are going to put "time-lapse"

00:03:01.809 --> 00:03:06.389
import media

00:03:06.389 --> 00:03:10.359
and since it's on our hard drive

00:03:10.359 --> 00:03:15.109
we are going to select this folder right here

00:03:15.109 --> 00:03:22.109
Select "Import"

00:03:32.249 --> 00:03:39.169
and as you can see all your media should be transferring right now

00:03:39.169 --> 00:03:46.169
create "New Project"

00:03:54.879 --> 00:03:56.419
and now

